## ğŸ“± React Component Integration

```astro
---
// In Astro files, use React components for interactivity
import DownloadButton from '../components/DownloadButton.jsx';
---

<main>
  <!-- Static content -->
  <h1>Welcome to Comfy</h1>
  
  <!-- Interactive React component -->
  <DownloadButton client:load />
</main>
```

### Client Directives
- `client:load` - Load immediately
- `client:idle` - Load when page is idle  
- `client:visible` - Load when component enters viewport
- `client:media` - Load based on media query

